?COMMENT white-fw HTTPS(8443)
ACCEPT          white		$FW	tcp	8443
HTTPS(ACCEPT)	white		$FW
allowinUPnP	white		$FW	# if white->fw is default DENY for uPnP
?COMMENT white-fw SSH
SSH(ACCEPT)	white		$FW

